        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "feat: cursor-based pagination for chat.history + fix partial NO_REPLY…",
        "body": "## Summary\r\n\r\n- Implements cursor-based pagination for `chat.history` so external consumers\r\n  (e.g. webchat) can load older messages page by page using a `before` index\r\n  parameter. Closes #19060.\r\n- Fixes partial `NO_REPLY` stream deltas (`\"NO_\"`, `\"NO_REPL\"`, etc.) being\r\n  committed as real assistant messages when a stream resolves to a silent reply.\r\n  Closes #13703.\r\n\r\n## Changes\r\n\r\n**Protocol / server**\r\n- `chat.history` accepts optional `before: integer` — returns messages before\r\n  that index\r\n- Response now includes `cursor` (first index returned) and `hasMore`\r\n- Cursor is recomputed after `capArrayByJsonBytes` / `enforceChatHistoryFinalBudget`\r\n  to stay accurate when leading messages are byte-capped (`droppedFromFront`)\r\n- Extracted `computeHistoryCursor` as a testable pure function\r\n\r\n**UI controller**\r\n- `ChatState` gains `chatCursor`, `chatHasMore`, `chatLoadingOlder`\r\n- `loadOlderChatHistory`: fetches the previous page, prepends messages, 500 ms\r\n  cooldown to avoid re-entry before scroll position restores\r\n- `handleChatEvent` delta branch: skips NO_REPLY deltas (preserves existing\r\n  stream); final/abort branches: also suppress partial NO_REPLY prefixes via\r\n  `isPartialSilentReply`\r\n\r\n**UI rendering**\r\n- Removed `CHAT_HISTORY_RENDER_LIMIT = 200` which silently discarded all\r\n  prepended older messages\r\n- \"Load older messages\" button rendered at the top of the thread when\r\n  `hasMore && onLoadOlder`\r\n- Scroll position compensated after prepend via `compensateChatScrollForPrepend`\r\n\r\n**Docs & tests**\r\n- `docs/gateway/protocol.md`: documents `before`, `cursor`, `hasMore`,\r\n  and byte-trimming behaviour\r\n- `chat.history.test.ts`: 10 unit tests for `computeHistoryCursor` and\r\n  `enforceChatHistoryFinalBudget`\r\n- `chat.test.ts`: 9 new cases covering pagination state, `loadOlderChatHistory`\r\n  lifecycle, and partial NO_REPLY suppression\r\n\r\n## Test plan\r\n\r\n- [x] `pnpm test ui/src/ui/controllers/chat.test.ts` — all 47 cases pass\r\n- [x] `pnpm test src/gateway/server-methods/chat.history.test.ts` — all 10 cases pass",
